      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the color pop in any light. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats are supple without a single crease, and the original factory protective films remain on several interior trim pieces. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a full portfolio of records included for your peace of mind. Mechanically, it is flawless\u2014the engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and it drives with the same precision, silence, and tightness as the day it rolled off the assembly line. No accidents, no smoking, and no stories. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a vehicle that has been treated with absolute reverence.",
